Package: hgnc.mcp
Title: MCP Server for HGNC Gene Nomenclature Resources
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Bulent Arman Aksoy
Maintainer: Bulent Arman Aksoy <arman@aksoy.org>
Authors@R:
    person("Bulent Arman", "Aksoy", , "arman@aksoy.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server for accessing
    HGNC (HUGO Gene Nomenclature Committee) gene nomenclature resources.
    Enables AI assistants to query gene symbols, names, and related information
    through a standardized protocol using plumber2mcp.
